Requirements List:
1.	The system shall allow the user the option to create an account.
  1.1.	The system shall display all the required fields to create an account.
    1.1.1.	 The system shall allow the user to create an account.
    1.1.2.	The system shall send an email to the user to confirm that the email is valid.
  1.2.	The system shall display confirmation of the account created.
2.	The system shall allow the user to login.
  2.1.	The system shall allow the user to input their username and password.
    2.1.1.	The system shall verify the username and password.
  2.2.	The system shall allow the user to recover a forgotten username or password.
    2.2.1.	 The system shall send an email displaying the user’s username.
    2.2.2.	The system shall send an email with a link to reset the user’s password.
3.	The system shall allow the user to post items.
  3.1.	The system shall allow the user to upload a picture for the item.
   3.2.	The system shall allow the user to take a picture for the item.
  3.3.	The system shall allow the user to assign a location for the item.
    3.3.1.	The system shall allow the user to create a new location.
  3.4.	The system shall allow the user to assign a category for the item.
    3.4.1.	 The system shall allow the user to create a new category for the item.
  3.5.	The system shall allow the user to assign a quantity for the item.
4.	The system shall allow The System shall correctly the identify the user's location within 0.5 mile.
  4.1.	The System shall provide capability to use the user's location provided by the user's browser location services.
    4.1.1.	 The System shall request permission to use the user's browser location services if not already granted.
    4.1.2.	 Given authorization, the system shall report the client's location using the browser's location services.
    4.1.3.	 The system shall display the user's location on the interface based on the reported location.


